## [Installable](installable/index.md)

The most recommended method of installation. Used when you want to install ${formal_name} to your machine.

## [Portable](portable/index.md)

Used when you want to run ${formal_name} on your machine without actually installing it.

## [Programmatic](programmatic/index.md)

Used when you want to use ${formal_name} programmatically. You can also use ${formal_name} CLI when installed this way.
